text pattern:
  contains:
  prefix: ^...
  suffix: ...$
  (ex: --prefix error r / --prefix warning y )
  (ex: --suffix ok g / --suffix fail r )
auto detect text pattern (not contains {[\(?+*) (optimizer)

more global option (--g-*): `--g-regex-type pcre pat1 colors , pat2 colors` intead of `--regex-type pcre pat1 colors , --regex-type pcre pat2 colors`

--utf8: utf8 pattern

optional label `?name` as color
